## 📂 Dataset

The dataset used in this project was prepared by compiling and integrating information from multiple official public sources. The raw data was collected, cleaned, validated, and merged into a unified dataset for analysis.

### Primary Data Sources

- Central Electricity Authority (CEA)
- POSOCO / Grid India
- Central Electricity Regulatory Commission (CERC)
- National Electricity Plan (NEP)
- NASA POWER Project (Weather Data)

The processed dataset is not included in this repository as it was manually curated and is reserved for future publication.
